\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Durban University of Technology a public higher education institution which has programmes that are accredited by the Council on Higher Education \'28CHE\'29 \line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of the Postgraduate Diploma in Hospitality Management programme which will be offered in the contact mode of delivery from the Durban\'2C Ritson Road\'2F Mansfield campus. \line \line The Institution is accredited to offer the following programmes\'3A\line - Higher Certificate in Hospitality and Leisure Studies H\'2FH04\'2FE105CAN \'28Contact mode of delivery\'29\line - Diploma in Hospitality Management H\'2FH04\'2FE108CAN \'28Contact mode of delivery\'29 \line - Advanced Diploma in Hospitality Management H\'2FH04\'2FE127CAN \'28Contact mode of delivery\'29\cell \pard 

